reviewText: Very old tape, but the message still valid, still the same....
Sorry video to watch, 1/3 of a star is not appropriate for this DVD

This short film was a very good purchase for me.  While teaching the dangers of driving under the influence of ANY substance, I am always looking for new teaching tools.  This film, even though dated, is surprisingly accurate about drivers today.  My clients were even surprised by how much they gained from watching this film.
